53#include "libfdt_env.h"
54
55#include <fdt.h>
56#include <libfdt.h>
57
58#include "libfdt_internal.h"
59
60int fdt_create_empty_tree(void *buf, int bufsize)
61{
62 int err;
63
64 err = fdt_create(buf, bufsize);
65 if (err)
66 return err;
67
68 err = fdt_finish_reservemap(buf);
69 if (err)
70 return err;
71
72 err = fdt_begin_node(buf, "");
73 if (err)
74 return err;
75
76 err = fdt_end_node(buf);
77 if (err)
78 return err;
79
80 err = fdt_finish(buf);
81 if (err)
82 return err;
83
84 return fdt_open_into(buf, buf, bufsize);
85}
